snippet.title: TRUE CRIME AND MAKEUP: THE UNSOLVED MURDER OF AMBER TUCCARO + HER FINAL CALL
snippet.description:
-TRUE CRIME AND MAKEUP: THE UNSOLVED MURDER OF AMBER TUCCARO + HER FINAL CALL

Hey guys welcome back to another true crime this is the unsolved murder of Amber Tuccaro a young native american woman who was murdered  in Canada I also have her final call that was recorded so grab a snack and lets talk True Crime and do some makeup :)

♡ If you have any sort of information regarding this case, please contact: Alberta RCMP at 780-412-5261 or Crime Stoppers at 1-800-222-TIPS (8477).

♡Source : https://thehueandcry.com/amber-tuccaro/

 ♡Justice for Amber facebook page https://www.facebook.com/JUSTICEFORAMBERTUCCARO/

♡ DISCLAIMER♡
I DID MY RESEARCH ONLINE FOR THIS VIDEO ALL INFORMATION I'VE SAID IN THIS VIDEO IS INFORMATION THAT WAS OUT  FOR THE PUBLIC. IF YOU THINK I'VE MISSED ANYTHING PLEASE SHARE IT WITH ME AND ILL DO MORE RESEARCH.

✰ PRODUCTS USED ✰ 
-EYEBROWS: https://www.ulta.com/precisely-my-brow-pencil-ultra-fine-shape-define?productId=xlsImpprod14191019
-CONCEALER: https://www.ulta.com/shape-tape-concealer?productId=xlsImpprod14251035
-FOUNDATION: https://www.ulta.com/natural-radiant-longwear-foundation?productId=xlsImpprod17421227
-EYESHADOW: https://www.anastasiabeverlyhills.com/jackie-aina-palette/ABH01-18184.html
-BLUSH: https://www.ulta.com/blush-trios?productId=xlsImpprod16211247
-LIPS: https://www.ulta.com/matte-lipstick?productId=xlsImpprod16451255

♡ I want to give credit to Bailey Sarian who inspired me to talk about theses unsolved cases and do my makeup i'm sure you know who she  is make sure to check out her channel https://www.youtube.com/user/makeupbyBAILEYSARIAN

♡ check out my true crime  and makeup playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLWPG7X5IJtXLNGO5SJVOh0F4E1Qgs-d_2
